Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my ultimate art...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I will detonate myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.54,0:00:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:13.41,Default,,0,0,0,,With death, I will become art.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.41,0:00:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,This never-before-seen explosion will leave\N a never-before-seen scar on this land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And...! My art will win\Nnever-before-seen admiration!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sorry, Tobi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.92,0:00:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,In the midst of my admiration,\Nyou will definitely die!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.31,0:00:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,This explosion will cover\Na ten-kilometer radius...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.80,0:00:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, tremble with fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Be in awe! Despair!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.59,0:00:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Scream!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.77,0:00:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,My art is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.50,0:01:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,An explosion!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.71,0:01:46.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What the--?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.71,0:02:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi, what is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.67,0:02:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This chakra...\NIt's that Akatsuki member...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.95,0:02:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.66,0:02:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.57,0:02:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.09,0:02:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke... It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.93,0:02:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't sense Sasuke's chakra!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.10,0:02:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's near our rendezvous point...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me he's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! It's just as I feared!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.07,0:02:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That Deidara...\NHe blew himself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Tobi?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably dead...\NHe was within the blast range...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.72,0:04:53.39,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(807.188,563.75)}Disappearance\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Deidara is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In the end, he went out with a bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.28,0:05:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.\NAnother member has been lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And I thought he was\Npretty strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.68,0:05:09.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Which one did him in?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke? Or the Nine-Tails' Jinchuriki?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.62,0:05:15.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Sasuke is dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Deidara took Sasuke down\Nwith him, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.78,0:05:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You should feel grateful, Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.31,0:05:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Deidara did you a favor\Nand got rid of your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... I feel like\Nwe've forgotten something...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.45,0:05:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Tobi is dead too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.85,0:05:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Deidara detonated himself\Nwithout regard for his surroundings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah yes, Tobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been quite a jutsu\Nif that chicken was unable to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter...\NHe can easily be replaced.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.81,0:06:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The loss of Deidara, however,\Nis unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.14,0:06:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I liked Tobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.07,0:06:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,When it came to lightening the mood\Nin our rather gloomy organization,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobi was quite talented.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall mourn Deidara's death in silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.11,0:06:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll mourn for Tobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You must really be bored, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,When the crest of\Nthe snake vanishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.51,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...I do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Add a drop of Sasuke's blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.14,0:06:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.43,0:06:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Summoning Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So, this is Orochimaru's\NSummoning Jutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.51,0:07:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Manda...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.24,0:07:08.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Orochimaru had trouble controlling him.\N How did Sasuke manage to...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.33,0:07:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. He used genjutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.04,0:07:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, you're a mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.84,0:07:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Who did you fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.22,0:07:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You...had the nerve...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:32.84,Default,,0,0,0,,to use me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.84,0:07:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You damned brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.09,0:07:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Those eyes...you controlled me...\Nwith those eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.09,0:07:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I...of all...people...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-ohh, he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.01,0:07:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't Manda Orochimaru's\Nfavorite pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.71,0:08:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You ought to treat animals better...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.58,0:08:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And the whole manipulation\Nwith the genjutsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.27,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There wasn't time to think.\NI had no choice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.64,0:08:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd be here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.43,0:08:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your chakra suddenly disappeared,\Nso I wondered what had happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you transport yourself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.07,0:08:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You hid yourself inside Manda,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.16,0:08:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,then used the Transportation Technique\Nto escape into another dimension...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,So why are you in such bad shape?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Just before escaping,\Nwe both got hit by the blast wave.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My opponent was one of the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He was stronger than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke all cut up and bruised\N{\i1}is also hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.54,0:08:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, he needs time to rest.\NRight, Karin?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem! How pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And you call yourself the man\Nwho killed Orochimaru?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.89,0:08:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru was already weakened\Nto begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.19,0:09:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.16,0:09:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It just won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.59,0:09:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strange to have this much rain\Naround here at this time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.04,0:09:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll ruin your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what someone as cold as you\Ncould be thinking about right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.07,0:09:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But from here,\Nyou look as though you are crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.28,0:09:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too bad about your younger brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.96,0:10:04.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You are now the sole survivor\Nof the Uchiha clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.04,0:10:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.13,0:10:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.51,0:10:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not dead. Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.54,0:10:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.71,0:10:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain...has stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.67,0:10:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it caught all our attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There are signs that Sasuke\Nwas just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's very faint,\Nbut his scent still lingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.83,0:10:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I also detect other scents.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.77,0:10:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:03.80,Default,,0,0,0,,From the damage to the terrain,\NI'd say there was a battle here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:10.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! One of the other scents belongs to that\N fellow in town on whom I detected Sasuke's scent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.79,0:11:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like there are others\Ntraveling alongside Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.59,0:11:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,He has a companion.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.83,0:11:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, back there...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.77,0:11:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probable that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.41,0:11:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke has formed his unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.42,0:11:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the five other scents belongs\Nto Deidara from Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he the one who self-destructed and was\N transported to another dimension by your jutsu, Sensei?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he faked\Nhis own death to escape...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The Akatsuki operate in two-man cells,\Nso there are three left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke is moving with\Na four-man cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares how many there are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get moving and\Ntrace Sasuke's scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.25,0:12:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The scent stops here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.71,0:12:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually in a situation like this,\N either Sasuke was blasted to bits by the explosion...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,or Sasuke used\Nthe Transportation Technique to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.14,0:12:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Transportation Technique...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.87,0:12:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably the latter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,My sense of smell is keener\Nthan a dog's right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.99,0:12:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've found Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.21,0:12:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A nose that's sharper than\N{\i1}the ninja hounds...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.56,0:12:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Impressive, Kiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what I would expect\N{\i1}from a member of the Inuzuka clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.41,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiba, lead the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.11,0:13:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And...what of Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.54,0:13:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming along nicely...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,He was using the Sharingan's power\Nto his fullest...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.41,0:13:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes will surpass Itachi's...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come.\NHe must be ready as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.32,0:13:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, he doesn't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.34,0:13:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what about the Nine-Tails?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.04,0:13:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You hunt it.\NAs leader, failure is not an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hah! You talked about killing Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to move\Nfor some time in that condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.43,0:14:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been moving nonstop lately.\NIt's a good chance to rest up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,All you've done is rest,\Nyou feeble punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.85,0:14:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,There, finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You did nothing at the northern hideout,\N so don't start telling me what to do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Wanna make something of it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.15,0:14:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.04,0:14:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu, Karin...\NHave you gathered data on Itachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.58,0:15:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in no shape to act so bossy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've picked up some tips about Akatsuki,\N but nothing specific about Itachi himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.51,0:15:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I got zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems they're targeting\Nspecific people though...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.97,0:15:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,People with special chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.02,0:15:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Special chakra...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.43,0:15:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I did some talking to animals and\Nlocated a number of Akatsuki hideouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems they always sense a powerful,\N unpleasant chakra around each area.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.42,0:15:42.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what the animals have told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.86,0:15:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, even simpleminded animals\Ncan sense chakra, eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.74,0:15:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Or maybe it's because\Nthey're simpleminded...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like you Karin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say, you jerk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.94,0:16:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu! This time,\Nyou're not getting away with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.92,0:16:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... W-Wait...hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill... I want to kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.83,0:16:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,- Huh?\N- Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.21,0:16:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot! Jugo's killing impulse is loose!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke! Hurry it--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.84,0:16:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Jugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.43,0:16:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault, Karin.\NScreaming and making such a fuss.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You too...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.40,0:17:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You constantly try to provoke me, Karin.\N What are you up to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.16,0:17:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.22,0:17:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't intend to leave Sasuke\Nfor my own reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not up to anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.15,0:17:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just trying to test your...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.25,0:17:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I...I need Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.14,0:17:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The only one who can\Nreplace Kimimaro...is Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke said he would\Nbecome my cage...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.06,0:18:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, only Sasuke can\Nstop my urges,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,like he did earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.40,0:18:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... I don't know about her,\Nbut our cages are unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.78,0:18:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We can escape anytime we wish.\NAnd yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure of it. It's this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.56,0:18:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,From his scent,\NI can tell he's stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.92,0:18:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems he's resting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.27,0:18:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:19:01.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...\N{\i1}Our paths have finally crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto Uzumaki...\NHe's no longer just a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He has now mastered a formidable jutsu\N and has many comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.25,0:19:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It won't be easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,He even destroyed two of\NKakuzu's lives with a single blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.28,0:19:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,To speak of the target as\Na threat has no meaning before Pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.92,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He has never lost a battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.63,0:19:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell the other members to hurry\Nwith the remaining Jinchuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,At last...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.37,0:19:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We are so close to the moment\Nof achieving our goal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.14,0:20:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Then everything shall be restored\Nto its rightful place...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.05,0:20:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The true power of the Sharingan...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.17,0:20:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The true power of I,\NMadara Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The sky is crying again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.07,0:20:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain... Are you...?
